trans-unit.source: Represents a security token handler that processes Kerberos tokens.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et token behandlingsprogram for sikkerhet som behandler Kerberos-token.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosSecurityTokenHandler"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosSecurityTokenHandler"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates whether the current instance can validate security tokens.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den gjeldende forekomsten kan validere sikkerhetstokener.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the handler can validate tokens of the type specified by the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosSecurityTokenHandler.TokenType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Angir om behandlingsprogrammet kan validere tokener som angis av den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosSecurityTokenHandler.TokenType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosSecurityTokenHandler.TokenType%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the handler can validate tokens; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis et behandlingsprogram kan validere tokener; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
Gets the Kerberos Security token type defined in WS-Security Kerberos Security Token profile.
trans-unit.target: Henter den Kerberos sikkerhet tokentypen definert i WS-Security Kerberos sikkerhetskode profilen.

trans-unit.source: The Kerberos Security token type URI.
By default, the value of the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenTypes.Kerberos%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Som standard verdien for den <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityTokenTypes.Kerberos%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the type of the token handled by the current instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter type token håndtert av den gjeldende forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: The type of the token handled by the current instance.
trans-unit.target: Typen for tokenet håndtert av den gjeldende forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: By default this is the type of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Som standard er typen for den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Validates the specified Kerberos security token.
The security token to be validated.
This must be an instance of the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Dette må være en forekomst av den <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The identities that are contained in the token.
The specified token is not assignable as a <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Det angitte tokenet kan ikke tilordnes som en <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosReceiverSecurityToken"> </xref>.
